posting_body: ['See better photos and', 'SCHEDULE A SHOWING', 'at:', '<URL>', "No, it's not a hyperlink.", ' :-(  You still have to copy-and-paste this link into the address bar on your web browser.', 'Beautiful 3 Bedroom Home', '2219 E 97th', 'St, Cleveland, OH, 44106', '$2750 per month', 'Available August 1st', '3 beds, 3 full and 1 half baths', '1754 sq.', 'ft.', 'Construction home, built in Feb 2022.', 'This contemporary, designer home features 10 ft ceilings on the 1st floor, abundant natural light with large windows and a wide open floor plan.', 'The 1st floor offers a spacious living room & dining room.', 'Modern kitchen with bright white cabinetry, appliances and a large island.', 'Laundry room with washer and dryer.', 'Half bath.', 'The 2nd floor offers 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms.', 'The large master suite has 2 walk-in closets and a master bath.', 'Finished basement with a full bathroom.', 'Vinyl flooring throughout the home.', 'Charming front porch.', 'Private backyard.', '2 car detached garage.', 'Street parking also available.', 'Short distance to Cleveland Clinic and close proximity to University Hospital, Case Western Reserve University and John Caroll.', 'Utilities and Extras', '.', 'Air conditioning', 'Lease Terms', '.', 'No pets', 'Contact Us:', 'Cleveland Property Management', 'show contact info', 'See better photos and', 'SCHEDULE A SHOWING', 'at:', '<URL>']
